Angela Levin claims the Duchess of Sussex had been given the "cold shoulder" by the streaming giant. A recent US tracker poll by Democracy Institute/ Express.co.uk found support for Ms Markle to enter politics was rising. In response to the findings, Ms Levin said: "Don't believe a word of it. It sounds like a verbal plaster to cover Meghan's disappointment at being cold-shouldered by Netflix. "In any case she is too thin skinned to take the hard criticism and investigations that a senior politician has to bear." FOLLOW BELOW FOR LIVE UPDATES...